    {
      "text": "Black Hole Assault is a 1992 fighting video game developed and published by Micronet for the Sega CD. It was released in Japan by Micronet, in North America by Bignet USA (Micronet's North American division) as a launch title for the system and in PAL territories by Sega. The game is the sequel to Micronet's Heavy Nova.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Blackhole Assault (orthographié Black Hole Assault au Japon) est un jeu vidéo de combat développé et édité par Micronet co., Ltd. en 1992 sur Mega-CD. Il a été porté en 1993 sur PC-Engine.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
